{"tid":1679712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講成立獨立調查委員會喇！","createTime":"2019-10-28T11:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T05:18:39.000Z","uid":131157,"like":25,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"278ee71960554482d5ccf2149ce011a5a80cfe6d","tid":1679712,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"陳雲：星期日講道。搵錢與不搵錢的分別。在政壇搵到大錢的人，會說成立獨立調查委員會，因為差人用來維持秩序，幫股市、幫地租，幫地產財閥及其他資本家即刻賺錢，蝕錢一陣都無法忍受，犯罪的差人也正好用來戴罪立功，加碼對付政敵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">差人已經去到戰爭罪犯那種非人的級數，還講獨立調查委員會？用現政權來做獨立調查？不是用革命政府、民主政府來做軍事法庭、人民法庭、紐倫堡大審判嗎？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">獨立調查委員會是維穩手段，共產黨在左推右推之後，會爽快答應香港愚民，因為一次輕判之後就不能用同樣罪名控告下一次（普通法的原則），好過特赦啊！</span></strong><br />\n不在政壇搵錢的人，也不理會什麼恢復秩序，會說報仇雪恨，此仇不報非君子。<br />\n一個錢字，分隔開兩種人。<br />\n我剛才講的，是孟子的義利之別。做人的大道理。不是成佛成仙，而是不墮落為餓鬼畜牲的大道理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157529272047225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157529272047225&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5y3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=c0a71cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157529272047225</a>/<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天滅中共，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2670d9c00a3e95f67aca785b24e83433bdb4b715","tid":1679712,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" 